==English==

===Etymology===
: (A proper name) Said to derive from the surname of Wilbur Clingan, who served with Gene Roddenberry in the Police Department.

===Pronunciation===
*klĭng'ŏn, /ˈklɪŋɒn/, /<tt>"klINQn</tt>/
*/ˈklɪŋɑn/, /<tt>"klINAn</tt>/<!-- cot-caught merger or just US-style IPA? -->

===Noun===
'''Klingon'''

#Member of an alien warrior race in the Star Trek universe, depicted as having distinctive forehead ridges, and a culture based on strict observance of honour, loyalty, and combat.
#Language spoken by (1) during Star Trek movies and episodes.

